<ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">akording tu dhe ingglis alfabet</ENAMEX>.") <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Two years ago</TIMEX>, the culture <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">ministers</ENAMEX> of
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Germany</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Austria</ENAMEX>, and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Switzerland</ENAMEX> agreed to simplify the <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">German</ENAMEX> language--among
