apply only to newly drafted documents and regulations--that is, to materials
promulgated on or after <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Oct. 1, 1998</TIMEX>, and <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Jan. 1, 1999</TIMEX>. But the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">president</ENAMEX>'s
