instructions" drafted prior to <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Oct. 1, 1998</TIMEX>, must be retroactively
rendered into <ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">Plain Language</ENAMEX>. Existing regulations also call for ex post facto
attention. Should the cleanup include all back issues of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Federal</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Register</ENAMEX> ? All presidential executive orders? <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Ford</ENAMEX>'s pardon of <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Nixon</ENAMEX>?
