            If
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">enforced</ENAMEX>, the <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">Plain Language Initiative</ENAMEX> would create a <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Year 2002 Problem of</ENAMEX>
