            Traditionally, the national
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">spelling bee</ENAMEX> is the venue where <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">immigrants</ENAMEX> triumphantly demonstrate
